                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360815-1877-offence-1 t18360815-cd-100"></join>6th of August</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360815-name-691" type="victimName">
